{"tid":1534163,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［全民運動］好警察表揚區","createTime":"2019-09-03T02:19:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T06:15:39.000Z","uid":305022,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"61f096051cc3c7291a8e6443b8287359a42c7c8e","tid":1534163,"uid":305022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T02:19:12.000Z","msg":"各位手足，我有一個諗法想大家集思廣益，靈感來自（塞爾維亞的民主運動）<br />\n<br />\n名稱 : 贊揚警察大行動<br />\n首先去某TG GROUP 或其他網站獲得警察居住地區資料和相片和名字<br />\n做法：用Ａ４紙（彩印佳）印其大頭並描述如&quot; 好警察陳大文&quot;並張貼在街上。（必須是該警察／警察家屬居住或上班的地區），其他乜黑警惡行乜都唔駛貼，只係貼大頭，舉例來說例如我番工會經過樓下大圍，落車地方係灣仔，咁就每日帶幾張大圍同灣仔既街招去貼，番工貼收工再貼。<br />\n<br />\n想法：人數非常重要，一人每天貼一張，達至片地開花之境況。因為運動過了兩個月，要歸邊都歸晒，但我想講其實就算你係街撞到個休班警你都認唔到。實際根本影響唔到警察既社區生活。<br />\n<br />\n張貼地方：任何當眼處，沒需要貼連農牆，用（白膠漿＋水）？定係其他噴霧式膠水<br />\n<br />\n我覺得的難題：<br />\n萬事起頭難，如何持之以恆，如何宣傳，如何做到撕一貼百，因為非連儂牆的地方一定會很容易被拆。我有諗過地區遊行果陣全世界行既時候順便貼埋。叫做起一個頭先，成個區都係某一兩個差佬既大頭都咪話唔哄動。<br />\n<br />\nＱ＆Ａ：<br />\n既然有連儂牆，為什麼要額外再貼？<br />\n我認為基本上去睇連儂牆的人都是中立偏黃，分享資訊為主，而且對警察壓力不大，純粹自嗨。<br />\n<br />\nＱ＆Ａ：<br />\n街招內容為什麼不直接寫黑警？<br />\n衝破普遍巿民不敢麻包袋心理關口，而且心理壓力較低，而且其實這街招就是讓巿民認人，而且重要的是能為該警帶來極大的心理壓力，我們這樣做不是抹黑。<br />\n<br />\n求各位巴絲集思廣益<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"917a2f058a498bfc43b8f619e50315752d1d6f48","tid":1534163,"uid":305022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T02:20:46.000Z","msg":"1/10"},{"pid":"d2a8f68431cad4001a1e1f6c252aabe3e9538fbc","tid":1534163,"uid":167619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T02:21:22.000Z","msg":"Gd idea<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GKH20p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GKH20p.png&h=6178433f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2386988e595d9ea1262f7b55883281410bd40a75","tid":1534163,"uid":167619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T02:21:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9fcc01351008476c45a5244e304ba51fdbed23c6","tid":1534163,"uid":305022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T02:21:39.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"097dba733213a000cbe8d9630f0f7946927ee626","tid":1534163,"uid":305022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T02:26:19.000Z","msg":"3/10"},{"pid":"ef59957fa8daa871a9a870066e35aedd425008ef","tid":1534163,"uid":305022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T02:28:56.000Z","msg":"4/10"},{"pid":"97e693d2c7d22ce673f3ceb3d9ff75cfab47a1b1","tid":1534163,"uid":305022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T02:33:06.000Z","msg":"5/10"},{"pid":"417983eeb025766327b8536f84ebe5689a52c4e8","tid":1534163,"uid":305022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T02:43:07.000Z","msg":"6/10"},{"pid":"335a88bf5253cb3cb6b3b115f426d47deea5e136","tid":1534163,"uid":305022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T02:57:17.000Z","msg":"7/10"},{"pid":"a3425434adfcf5ca156091fad9da5755cff0b657","tid":1534163,"uid":251207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T02:59:43.000Z","msg":"P牌推唔郁 幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8f985264ad10b21772980dff6fb634a2a2e9a84","tid":1534163,"uid":305022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T03:05:10.000Z","msg":"8/10"},{"pid":"bb72ab655aabd34d518f6006a63ddc54f4597e1a","tid":1534163,"uid":305022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T03:17:04.000Z","msg":"9/10"},{"pid":"80ad55071fedf7446eeb4c0ee3733b7dbcf6ba63","tid":1534163,"uid":305022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T06:15:39.000Z","msg":"10/10"}]}